items.badge_description: Happy St. Patrick's Day to you! No matter what you're drinking today, from the rarest of barrel ages stouts to the lightest of green-colored lagers, may the luck of the Irish be with you!
Light and crisp, a Pilsner is all you need to make your day great. Though, perhaps another one would make it even better. Thats 15 different Pilsners. Try 5 more to unlock Level 4.
